three upgrades: CSV export, tagging & tag filters, and a Smart Bundle generator. Drop this whole file in LCFG-4.5-Advanced.html and open locally.

What‚Äôs new
	‚Ä¢	CSV Export: exports selected cards (or all, on confirm) with full columns.
	‚Ä¢	Tagging: add/remove tags to selected; tag cloud; filter by tags (AND).
	‚Ä¢	Smart Bundle: enter a goal (e.g., ‚Äújurisdiction challenge‚Äù), pick a size; it auto-scores cards by Title/Core/Model/Tags and selects the best. Instantly builds your bundle.

